fields.name: Administration
fields.description: A collection of Dedicated capacity administrators

fields.name: Mode
fields.description: Specifies the generation of the Power BI Embedded capacity. If no value is specified, the default value 'Gen2' is used. [Learn More](https://docs.microsoft.com/power-bi/developer/embedded/power-bi-embedded-generation-2)

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The current deployment state of PowerBI Dedicated resource. The provisioningState is to indicate states for resource provisioning.

fields.name: State
fields.description: The current state of PowerBI Dedicated resource. The state is to indicate more states outside of resource provisioning.

fields.name: TenantId
fields.description: Tenant ID for the capacity. Used for creating Pro Plus capacity.
